originalText.text: Left my car with them in the morning, I come to pick it up around evening time with my drivers side mirror broken and hanging off. No one wanted to take responsibility for it, did not even compensate me for the day paid to park there. They even tried to “fix” it and broke it even more. Last time i ever use there services again. you want to pay cheap? Expect to get cheap back.

The worst customer experience ever. Staff there is extremely rude and aggressive.
When I showed my reservation number on my phone, he rejected it like some dirty thing and bossed around like "read the number." I had a soar throat so I wrote the number on a piece of paper to hand it over to him. He rejected the paper as well and told me to "read the number" again. When I confronted him why he wouldn't take neither my phone nor my paper, he got super aggressive and started yelling at my face (like his face was an inch away from mine). I felt very intimidated. I demanded a refund and it got rejected as well.
